info.author: Mandela Logan
info.name: aisak
info.summary: AISAK, short for Artificially Intelligent Swiss Army Knife, is a state-of-the-art language model designed for text generation tasks. Developed by Mandela Logan, this Large Language Model (LLM) is fine-tuned on extensive datasets to excel in understanding and interpreting your various queries in natural language text.

info.author: Mandela Logan
info.name: aisak
info.summary: AISAK, short for Artificially Intelligent Swiss Army Knife, is a general-purpose AI system comprising various models designed for different tasks. Developed by the AISAK team, one of the models within AISAK is a state-of-the-art language model designed for text generation tasks. This package leverages usage of the model, named AISAK-Assistant, which is fine-tuned on extensive datasets to excel in understanding and interpreting various queries in natural language text.
